    <item>
      <title>法院称，德克萨斯州可以逮捕并驱逐非法穿越墨西哥边境的人</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/25/us/texas-mexico-border-arrest-deport-immigration.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法院暂停了 2023 年一项允许州和地方警察逮捕移民的法律，现在已裁定该措施合法，这一决定可能会被上诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/25/us/texas-mexico-border-arrest-deport-immigration.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 25 Apr 2026 19:40:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
